## i18n (next-intl)

- **All user-facing text MUST use translations** ‚Äî no hardcoded strings
- Translation files: `messages/vi.json`, `messages/en.json`
- Use `useTranslations()` hook in client components
- Use `getTranslations()` in server components
- Locale routing: `/vi/...`, `/en/...` via `app/[locale]/`
- Default locale: `vi`

```js
const t = useTranslations();
// CORRECT:
<p>{t('post.noStories')}</p>
// WRONG:
<p>Kh√¥ng c√≥ b√Ýi vi·∫øt n√Ýo</p>
```

