## TipTap Extension System

- **Base extensions** defined in `utils/tiptapBaseExtensions.js` via `getBaseExtensions(imageExtension)` factory
- **Client** uses `utils/tiptapExtensions.js` ‚Üí `getExtensions()` = `getBaseExtensions(ImageBlock)` (with ReactNodeViewRenderer)
- **Server** uses `utils/renderContentServer.js` ‚Üí `getBaseExtensions(ImageBlockServer)` (no React dependency)
- When adding a new extension: add it to `tiptapBaseExtensions.js` ONCE ‚Äî both client and server get it automatically
- See `.cursor/rules/editor-rule.mdc` for detailed editor conventions

