## Naming Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|-----------|---------|
| Components | PascalCase | `PostList`, `BasePostItem` |
| Hooks | camelCase with `use` prefix | `useInfinitePosts`, `useAuth` |
| Service functions | camelCase verb-first | `getPosts`, `createPost`, `fetchUserPosts` |
| Utils | camelCase | `renderPostContent`, `combineClasses`, `formatDate` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `USER_ROLES`, `PAGE_SIZE` |
| CSS variables | kebab-case with `--` prefix | `--text-muted`, `--bg-surface` |
| Files | PascalCase for components, camelCase for hooks/utils/services | `PostList.js`, `useAuth.js`, `postService.js` |

### Service function naming
- `get*` ‚Äî fetch single/paginated public data
- `fetch*` ‚Äî fetch data (legacy, prefer `get*` for new code)
- `create*` ‚Äî POST new resource
- `update*` ‚Äî PUT/PATCH existing resource
- `delete*` ‚Äî DELETE resource

---

## Performance Guidelines

- Use `dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })` for heavy client components (editor, publish panel)
- Limit Framer Motion animations on long lists ‚Äî only animate newly loaded items (see `PostList.js` `prevCountRef` pattern)
- Use `dedupingInterval` in SWR to prevent duplicate API calls
- Avoid `will-change` on many elements
- Use `React.memo()` only when profiling shows unnecessary re-renders ‚Äî don't prememo everything
- When extracting sub-components that receive callbacks as props, wrap the callbacks in `useCallback` in the parent to avoid unnecessary re-renders

---

## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

1. **Do NOT copy-paste `useSWRInfinite` boilerplate** ‚Äî always use `useInfiniteList` or `useInfiniteCursor`
2. **Do NOT hand-roll skeletons/error states/empty states** ‚Äî use shared components
3. **Do NOT hand-roll avatar circles** ‚Äî use `<Avatar>` from `UI/`
4. **Do NOT hand-roll inline spinners** ‚Äî use `<Spinner>` from `UI/Loading`
5. **Do NOT hand-roll click-outside listeners inline** ‚Äî use `useOutsideClick` hook
6. **Do NOT hand-roll `body.style.overflow = 'hidden'` in modals** ‚Äî use `useBodyScrollLock` hook
7. **Do NOT hand-roll scroll listeners for sticky nav** ‚Äî use `useScrollEffect` hook
8. **Do NOT hand-roll `input[type=file]` + upload logic** ‚Äî use `useFileUpload` hook
9. **Do NOT use named imports for axios instances** ‚Äî they are default exports
10. **Do NOT hardcode Vietnamese/English strings in JSX** ‚Äî use `next-intl` translations
11. **Do NOT create duplicate service functions** for the same endpoint
12. **Do NOT duplicate extension lists** ‚Äî use `tiptapBaseExtensions.js` factory
13. **Do NOT use `findIndex` for deduplication** ‚Äî use `Set` for O(n) performance
14. **Do NOT create 900-line utility files** ‚Äî split into focused modules under a directory
15. **Do NOT store functions in React state** without wrapping: `setState(() => fn)` not `setState(fn)`
16. **Do NOT mix 3 styling approaches in one component** ‚Äî be consistent
17. **Do NOT import `Post/PostSkeleton`** ‚Äî this file no longer exists. Use `Post/PostItemSkeleton` (timeline feed) or `Shared/PostSkeleton` (multi-variant)

